/************************
  ** OCaml Installation 
  ***********************/
For detail see the website: http://ocamldt.free.fr/spip.php?article5
(1) Download and install ODT (OCaml Development Tools) for Mac
    (download site: http://caml.inria.fr/download.en.html)
(2) Install ODT
    Help > Install New Software > Add ""http://odt.sf.net"" > Install ODT
(3) Set the OCaml compiler
    Eclipse > Preferences > OCaml > Compiler > compiler folder "/usr/local/bin"

(4) Manage the builder profiles
    Right click the OCaml project > Properties > OCaml > Executables, Libraries > Executables > 
    Add > /- Target name: can be any name labeling the compiling resulting executable file
          |- Target folder: denote where to put the compiling resulting file
	  |- Source file: the OCaml file .ml to be compiled
	  |- Builder profile: select the default one

(5) print_string: to print an string
    print_int: to print an int

    for example: # print_string "Hello world!\n";; 

